Dependencies: python-mpd, BeautifulSoup (install using pip or your package manager) 

To install, run ./install_script.sh and restart XChat; or load ~/xchat2/xchat_lastfm.py and ~/xchat2/xchat_mpd.py py at the XChat Menu Window > Plugins and Scripts > Load

To use just type /mpd or /lastfm at xchat

